<h1>Create a song!</h1>
<form action="/songs/new" method="post">
  <input type="text" name="song_name" id="Name">
  <br/><br/>
  
  <p>Select an artist:</p>
  <p><%@artists.each do |a|%>
    <input type="radio" name="existing_artist" value="<%=a.name%>" id="Artist"><label for="existing_artist"> <%=a.name%></label>
  <%end%></p>
  <p>Or, create a new artist.</p>
  <label for="new_artist">Artist name: </label><input type="text" name="new_artist" id="Artist Name">
  <br/><br/>
  
  <p>Select one or more genres:</p>
  <p><%@genres.each do |g|%>
    <input type="checkbox" name="existing_genre" id="<%=g.name%>"><label for="existing_genre"> <%=g.name%></label>
  <%end%></p>
  <p>Or, create a new genre.</p>
  <label for="new_genre">Genre name: </label><input type="text" name="new_genre" id="Genre">
  
  <p><input type="submit" value="Create song!" id="Create"></p>
</form>